data.description: A LOT Custom Features!! Two-story foyer with open concept floor plan. The kitchen offers a large island with bar height seating. Media room, office with custom-built barn doors with custom desk, formal dr, wide plank flooring. 20 ft wide custom waterfall made with natural local rock, large fire pit with built-in seating, custom outdoor kitchen, with granite countertops, including a Weber gas grill and 36-inch flat top griddle. Professionally designed landscaping.Extra-wide driveway that fits 3 oversized vehicles. The subdivision offers a huge swimming pool with water slide and tennis.
